# 材料研究：炼化锭
planarartifice.research.matstudy_alkimium.title=材料研究：炼化锭
planarartifice.research.matstudy_alkimium.stage.1.text=或许炼化锭也能作为傀儡的材料。将质地柔软轻盈的黄铜用在傀儡上，其中的好处也都彰显了出来，但炼化锭又会带来怎样的体验呢？
planarartifice.research.matstudy_alkimium.complete.text=经过进一步研究，似乎使用炼化锭制作出的傀儡移动时会更加轻盈迅速...但它们的动作好像有些奇怪。
#planarartifice.research.MATSTUDYALKIMIUM.title=Material Studies: Alkimium
#planarartifice.research.MATSTUDYALKIMIUM.stage.1.text=While alkimium is more brittle than brass, it is much more resistant to heat and explosions.<BR>Its color stands out against most backgrounds, and retains brass' lightness. It should be an improvement over plain brass, so long as it isn't being hit.
